<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
    <title>FAQs | VASKA</title>
</head>
<body class="px-16 tracking-wide bg-[#FAF8F0] text-[#1e1e19] font-[Montserrat]">
    <%- include('partials/topbar') %>
    
    <div class="container mx-auto my-10 p-6 bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)</h1>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">Find answers to common questions about shopping, orders, payments, and more.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">1. How can I track my order?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Once your order is shipped, you will receive a tracking number via email. You can also track your order in the "My Orders" section of your account.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">2. What payment methods do you accept?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">We accept major credit/debit cards, net banking, UPI, and wallet payments. Cash on Delivery (COD) is also available for select locations.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">3. How can I cancel my order?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">You can cancel your order before it is shipped by visiting the "My Orders" section. If the order has already been dispatched, you may return it after delivery.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">4. What is the return policy?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">We offer a 14-day return policy for most products. Items must be unused and in original packaging. Visit our <a href="/returns-exchange" class="text-blue-600 underline">Returns & Exchange</a> page for details.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">5. How do I use a discount code?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">During checkout, enter your discount code in the designated field and click "Apply." The discount will be reflected in your order summary.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">6. How can I contact customer support?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">You can reach us via email, phone, or live chat. Visit our <a href="/contact" class="text-blue-600 underline">Contact Us</a> page for details.</p>
    </div>
    
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
